title: Welsh Fairy Tales and Other Stories
creator: P.H. Emerson
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Welsh Fairy Tales and Other Stories by P.H. Emerson. These tales were collected by me whilst living in Anglesea during the winter 1891-2. With the exception of the French story, they were told me and I took them down at the time. In most cases I have done but little "editing", preferring to give the stories as told. P. H. Emerson, April 1894. (Summary from Author's Note) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. M4B format available
